{
  "stem": "13483.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 18.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was only with the American forces for about two or three weeks, with the American Ninth Army.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And after-- I left the American Ninth.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I went back to our-- not regiment-- to our division, that we went onto Munster.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No idea.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's a very difficult thing--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I really don't remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it must've been.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, I think after that, we went on to Brunswick or Hannover.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Days, you know?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not any length of time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The officers had maps.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But not the ordinary sap or private soldier.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yeah, of course we knew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we'd heard about them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course we had.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you've got to remember, we had army newspapers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] We had American newspapers, army newspapers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, we read it from there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course the mere fact that I heard from my friends, the Esses, we'd learned-- we'd learned quite a bit.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, what happened to the Jewish population, and all that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, after were-- we were already aware of the concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were aware of them and what the Germans were doing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I couldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think they felt the same as I did.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We felt, obviously, quite a lot of hatred to the Germans, especially what they'd done in France and Belgium.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we'd heard all about that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I've still got letters form my wife and all that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And funnily enough, it wasn't mentioned.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe because of the censors.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because your mail was censored at a time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But of course, I-- you couldn't always write.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You weren't allowed to say where you were.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
